var armProfile = allProfile["resource-manager"];
foreach (var keyValuePair in armProfile)
{
    var namespaceName = keyValuePair.Key;
    var element = keyValuePair.Value;
    // ... rest stays the same
```

Replace with:
```csharp
var span = BinaryData.FromStream(stream).ToMemory();
using var doc = JsonDocument.Parse(span);
var armProfile = doc.RootElement.GetProperty("resource-manager");
foreach (var keyValuePair in armProfile.EnumerateObject())
{
    var namespaceName = keyValuePair.Name;
    var element = keyValuePair.Value;
    // ... rest stays the same (element is already JsonElement, so EnumerateObject/EnumerateArray work)
```

Note: `BinaryData.FromStream(stream).ToMemory().Span` is used with `JsonSerializer.Deserialize<T>(ReadOnlySpan<byte>)`. When switching to `JsonDocument.Parse`, use `ReadOnlyMemory<byte>` (`.ToMemory()` without `.Span`), since `JsonDocument.Parse` accepts `ReadOnlyMemory<byte>`.

## 6. Four LRO files

These four files all have the SAME code on line 61 in their `GetOperationId` method:
```csharp
